### ============================================================
### COINBASE CLONE API — REST Client Test File
### Install "REST Client" VS Code extension to run these
### ============================================================

@base = http://localhost:5000
@contentType = application/json


### ============================================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================================

GET {{base}}/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### ============================================================
### AUTH — REGISTER
### ============================================================

POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Alice Johnson",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Register admin (manually set role in DB after registering)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "adminpassword123"
}


### ============================================================
### AUTH — LOGIN
### ============================================================

POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as admin
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "adminpassword123"
}


### ============================================================
### AUTH — PROFILE (protected)
### Requires cookie from login — works automatically in REST Client
### ============================================================

GET {{base}}/api/auth/profile
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### ============================================================
### AUTH — LOGOUT
### ============================================================

POST {{base}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### ============================================================
### CRYPTO — GET ALL (public, paginated)
### ============================================================

GET {{base}}/api/crypto
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### With pagination
GET {{base}}/api/crypto?page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### ============================================================
### CRYPTO — TOP GAINERS
### ============================================================

GET {{base}}/api/crypto/gainers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Top 5 gainers
GET {{base}}/api/crypto/gainers?limit=5
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


### ============================================================
### CRYPTO — NEWEST COINS
### ============================================================

GET {{base}}/api/crypto/new
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Newest 3 coins
GET {{base}}/api/crypto/new?limit=3
Content-Type: {{contentType}}


